com.judopay.api

Class ApiError

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.judopay.api.ApiError
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class ApiError
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    A single error instance that occurred when calling the judo API, in response to performing a request, most likely for a type of transaction such as a payment, pre-auth or token payment.
